Module edu.wgu.tmaama
Package edu.wgu.tmaama.db.Salt.model

Class Salt

java.lang.Object
edu.wgu.tmaama.db.Salt.model.Salt
public class Salt extends Object
Database model for Salts table. A salt is a term used for hashing sensitive information (namely passwords) so that we don't have to store a user's password directly. Rather we store the hash and the salt used to hash the password so that if the database was to be leaked the chance of a user being hacked is less likely.
